Description: HPE Nimble Storage integration for Proxmox VE
 This package provides a Perl library to integrate HPE Nimble Storage
 arrays with Proxmox VE storage management over iSCSI.
 .
 It allows administrators to configure and manage Nimble volumes
 directly within Proxmox VE (create, delete, resize, snapshots).
 Supports Proxmox VE 8.2+.
